[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15549] Fixed a chrono panic and hotfix
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15544] Bugfix: datetime parsing and local timezones
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15522] Fixed wrong display of human-readable strings
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15495] Moved human date parsing into a new command 
``date from-human``
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15455] Added the ability to construct datetime from a record
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15447] Replaced some 
``PipelineMismatch``
 errors with 
``OnlySupportsThisInputType``
 shell errors
sholderbach:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15541] Bumped 
``crossbeam-channel``
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15519] Fixed future clippy lints
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15515] Fixed Exbibyte parsing
blindFS:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15540] Fixed LSP command name highlighting/renaming for better accuracy
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15523] Fixed several edge cases of inaccurate references in LSP
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15517] Improved parser_info-based ID detection for 
``use``
/
``overlay``
 keywords in LSP
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15514] Fixed workspace-wide operations that could panic in certain conditions
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15508] Refactored LSP to align markdown doc strings with 
``--help``
 output
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15499] Fixed keyword handling in LSP completion snippets
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15494] Added snippet-style completion for commands in LSP
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15470] Improved PWD accuracy in LSP: from env to the parent dir of the current file
pyz4:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15538] Added a new 
``polars``
 command: 
``polars replace-time-zone``
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15490] Fixed 
``polars as-datetime``
 to respect timezone information
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15473] Made 
``polars into-df``
/
``polars into-lazy``
's 
``--schema``
 option more lenient
fdncred:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15537] Fixed 
``datetime-diff``
 to report milliseconds, microseconds, and nanoseconds
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15498] Reverted a fix for 
``table -e``
 wrapping issue
ayax79:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15534] Introduced 
``polars into-schema``
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15529] Added 
``NuDataType``
 and the 
``polars dtype``
 command
